t running or dies then the Analysis daemon just writes them itself.
\par }{\b\insrsid7562726 zms}{\insrsid7562726  - This is the ZoneMinder Streaming server. The web interface connects with this to get real-time or historical streamed images.}{\insrsid998625  It runs only when a live monitor stream 
