\par }\pard \s15\qj \li360\ri0\sa180\widctlpar\nooverflow\faroman\rin0\lin360\itap0 {\b\insrsid7562726 zmpkg.pl}{\insrsid7562726  - This is the ZoneMinder Package Control script. This is used by the web interface and service scripts to
